filament_end_gcode:
; Filament-specific end gcode 
;END gcode for filament
filament_notes:
Set with temperature tower to 220
Checks out for yellow, bone and black
filament_start_gcode:
; filament gcode
{if printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_OS_KLIPPER.*/ and printer_notes=~/.*HOTEND_AFTERBURNER_E3D.*/ and nozzle_diameter[0]==0.4} SET_PRESSURE_ADVANCE ADVANCE=0.0615 {endif}  ; AB 2021-10-05
{if printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_OS_KLIPPER.*/ and printer_notes=~/.*HOTEND_SWITCH_E3D.*/ and nozzle_diameter[0]==0.4} SET_PRESSURE_ADVANCE ADVANCE=0.38{endif}  ;GUESS Switchwire Bowden
{if printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_OS_KLIPPER.*/ and printer_notes=~/.*HOTEND_AFTERBURNER_E3D.*/ and printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_NOZZLE_CHT*/ and nozzle_diameter[0]==0.6} SET_PRESSURE_ADVANCE ADVANCE=0.045{endif}  ; 2022-02-18
name: eSun PLA+ @CHT
